record.name: IP Address
record.description: This service is to order a static IP address from an HP subnet. Static IP addresses are normally used for Printers, Workstations or LAN/WAN hardware. For Personal Computers or Notebooks, we strongly recommend using the 'Dynamic IP address' (DHCP) service.
